Zvi Galil
Zvi Galil
Zvi Galil is the Julian Clarence Levi
Professor of 
Mathematical Methods and Computer Science at the 
Computer Science Department
of 
Columbia University
 in the city of New York. He currently serves as the Morris A. and
Alma Schapiro Professor and Dean of the 
School of Engineering and Applied Science at Columbia University.
His main research interests are in the design and
analysis of 
algorithms, 
computational complexity
 and 
cryptography.  Zvi is the Editor in Chief of
SIAM Journal on Computing and the
Journal of Algorithms. 
